{{Infobox sports league |current_season = 2015 Bucharest Trophy |sport=[[Handball]] |founded=2014 |teams=6 |champion={{flagicon|ROU}} [[CSM Bucharest (women's handball)|CSM Bucharest]] }}
The '''Bucharest Trophy''' ({{lang-ro|Trofeul București}}) is a pre-season international women's [[Handball|team handball]] tournament for clubs, held each year in [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]]. The competition is hosted by [[Liga Naţională (Handbal Feminin)|Liga Naţională]] club [[CSM Bucharest (women's handball)|CSM Bucharest]] at the [[Polyvalent Hall (Bucharest)|Sala Polivalentă]] and governed by the rules and regulations of the [[International Handball Federation|IHF]]. It is currently contested by six teams. The event, inaugurated in 2014, is considered the most prestigious annual friendly tournament that takes place in Romania.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmbucuresti.ro/club/513-live-blog-bucharest-trophy-2014-viborg-vine-la-bucuresti|title=LIVE BLOG Bucharest Trophy 2014: Viborg vine la București!|publisher=[[CSM București (Women's Handball)|CSM București]]|date=9 May 2014|language=Romanian|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512222353/http://www.csmbucuresti.ro/club/513-live-blog-bucharest-trophy-2014-viborg-vine-la-bucuresti|archivedate=12 May 2014|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prosport.ro/alte-sporturi/handbal/final-4-ul-ligii-campionilor-se-muta-in-bucuresti-csm-bucuresti-aduce-buducnost-in-romania-si-asteapta-o-confirmare-si-de-la-gyor-12349974|title=Final 4-ul Ligii Campionilor se "mută" în Bucureşti. CSM Bucureşti aduce Buducnost în România şi aşteaptă o confirmare şi de la Gyor|publisher=[[Prosport]]|date=28 March 2014|language=Romanian}}</ref>
