{{infobox country at games | NOC = KUW | NOCname = [[Kuwait Olympic Committee]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1992 | flagcaption = | oldcode = | website = {{url|www.kuwaitolympic.net }}&nbsp;{{ar icon}} {{en icon}} | location = [[Barcelona]] | competitors = 32 | sports = 7 | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = {{flagIOC|IOA|2016 Summer}} (2016) }}
'''[[Kuwait]]''' competed at the '''[[1992 Summer Olympics]]''' in [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]]. 32 competitors, all men, took part in 18 events in 7 sports.<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/KUW/summer/1992/ |title=Kuwait at the 1992 Summer Games |accessdate=2011-12-26 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>
