'''Men's Javelin Throw''' *[[Ghanim Mabrouk]] :* Qualification &mdash; NM (→ did not advance)
'''Men's Hammer Throw''' *[[Waleed Al-Bakheet]] :* Qualification &mdash; 63.94 m (→ did not advance)
