'''Sporting Vereniging Notch''' is a Surinamese football club based in [[Moengo]], [[Marowijne District|Marowijne]]. The club presently competes in the [[Hoofdklasse (Suriname)|Surinamese Hoofdklasse]], the top tier of [[Football in Suriname|Surinamese football]]. Notch earned promotion into the Hoofdklasse after winning the [[Surinamese Eerste Klasse]], the second tier of Surinamese football.<ref>{{cite web|title=Eerste Klasse: Suriname (Table)|url=https://int.soccerway.com/national/surinam/eerste-klasse/2010-2011/regular-season/tables/|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=9 August 2011}}</ref> The club kit manufacturer is [[Jako]].

