{{BLP sources|date=May 2012}} {{unreliable sources|date=May 2012}} {{Infobox football biography | name = Vanquever Frett | image = | fullname = Vanquever Frett | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1983|11|11|df=y}} | birth_place = [[British Virgin Islands]] | height = | position = [[Defender (football)|Defender]] | currentclub = | clubnumber = | youthyears1 = |youthclubs1 = | years1 = |clubs1 = |caps1 = |goals1 = | pcupdate = 4 January 2012 | nationalyears1 = 2011–2015 | nationalteam1 = [[British Virgin Islands national football team|British Virgin Islands]] | nationalcaps1 = 5 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | ntupdate = 15 June 2018 }}
'''Vanquever Frett''' (born 11 November 1983) in the [[British Virgin Islands]] is a [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Defender (football)|Defender]]. He currently plays for the [[British Virgin Islands national football team]].
== Personal life == Vanquever's brother, Vesquever Frett, also plays for the [[British Virgin Islands national football team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://caribbeanfootballdatabase.com/britishvirginislands/players/vesqueverfrett.html|title=Vesquever Frett - British Virgin Islands - Caribbean Football|work=caribbeanfootballdatabase.com}}</ref>
==International career== On 3 July 2011, he made his debut for the [[British Virgin Islands national football team]] in a World Cup 2014 Qualifier match against [[US Virgin Islands national football team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://caribbeanfootballdatabase.com/britishvirginislands/players/vanqueverfrett.html|title=Vanquever Frett - British Virgin Islands - Caribbean Football|work=caribbeanfootballdatabase.com}}</ref>
